{
  "stem": "3085.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, we were a middle-class family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wouldn't consider ourselves wealthy people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we were certainly well off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had a business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he-- we certainly didn't lack any of the-- of the essentials of life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was selling automotive parts, which, of course, back in the-- when they started that business in, in the 1920s.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were very few automobiles in Hungary in the 1920s.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was one of the first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, I think he was the first in town selling cars and, and, and, and automotive parts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had a Ford-- he was a representative of Ford.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was, I think, the European Ford.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't the American Ford.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And other-- he had other representations as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he did very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And unfortunately, of course, his business was confiscated, taken away, first, by the Germans, and then, by the Communists after the war.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he lost his business twice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it's-- he never really-- after losing his business, he never really became-- you know, he did OK.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he was not-- never the same anymore, as far as financially or, or business-wise.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a young boy, we went to a-- both my brother and I, and my sister, too, of course-- we went to a Jewish elementary school, the only Jewish elementary school in Pecs.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a four year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The school system there was, of course, four years elementary school and then what was called 'gymnasium,' which is the equivalent of a high school in Canada, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The eight grades of high school, of gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went-- after completing the four-year elementary school, Jewish elementary school, we were enrolled in, in a private gymnasium run by the Cistercian Order of priests.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
